'''梅杜莎槽沟层'''(Medusae Fossae Formation)是[[火星|火星]]上一处可能起源于[[火山|火山]]的大型地质单元<ref name=esa-mff>{{cite web|title=The Medusa Fossae formation on Mars|url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Mars_Express/The_Medusa_Fossae_formation_on_Mars/(print)|publisher=[[European_Space_Agency|European Space Agency]]|date=29 March 2005|access-date=2020-11-24|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622004837/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Mars_Express/The_Medusa_Fossae_formation_on_Mars/(print)|dead-url=no}}</ref>，它取名自[[希腊神话|希腊神话]]中的[[美杜莎|梅杜莎]]，而”槽沟”(Fossa)一词是[[拉丁语|拉丁语]]“深沟”之意。该地貌约位于南纬5°、东经213°处，横跨[[塔尔西斯|塔尔西斯]]和[[埃律西昂|埃律西昂]]火山区附近的[[火星分界|高-低地边界]]区，其范围涵盖[[亚马孙区_(火星)|亚马逊区]]、[[塔尔西斯区|塔尔西斯区]]、[[门农区|门农区]]、[[埃律西昂区|埃律西昂区]]和[[埃俄利斯区|埃俄利斯区]]等五大区域的部分地区。

==地质==
梅杜莎槽沟层为沿火星[[赤道|赤道]]绵延(不连续)超过5000公里的松软、易风化沉积区，其面积相当于美国大陆面积的20%<ref name=pmid30030425>{{cite journal |doi=10.1038/s41467-018-05291-5 |pmid=30030425 |pmc=6054634 |title=The Medusae Fossae Formation as the single largest source of dust on Mars |journal=Nature Communications |volume=9 |issue=1 |pages=2867 |year=2018 |last1=Ojha |first1=Lujendra |last2=Lewis |first2=Kevin |last3=Karunatillake |first3=Suniti |last4=Schmidt |first4=Mariek |bibcode=2018NatCo...9.2867O }}</ref>。有时，该地层看起来像一片起伏平缓的平地，但在一些地方，因风蚀而形成了大片山脊和沟槽地形<ref name=esa-mff/>。雷达成像显示，该地区可能含有极多孔岩石(例如[[火山灰|火山灰]])或类似[[冰川_(火星)|冰川]]的厚冰层，其数量与火星南极[[冰盖|冰盖]]下的储量大致相同<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1126/science.1148112 |pmid=17975034 |lay-url=https://www.newscientist.com/article/dn12866-vast-amount-of-water-ice-may-lie-on-martian-equator/ |laysource=NewScientist |laydate=November 1, 2007 |title=Radar Sounding of the Medusae Fossae Formation Mars: Equatorial Ice or Dry, Low-Density Deposits? |journal=Science|volume=318 |issue=5853|pages=1125–1128 |year=2007|last1=Watters|first1=T. R. |last2=Campbell|first2=B. |last3=Carter|first3=L. |last4=Leuschen|first4=C. J. |last5=Plaut|first5=J. J. |last6=Picardi|first6=G. |last7=Orosei|first7=R. |last8=Safaeinili|first8=A. |last9=Clifford|first9=S. M. |last10=Farrell|first10=W. M. |last11=Ivanov|first11=A. B. |last12=Phillips|first12=R. J. |last13=Stofan|first13=E. R. |bibcode=2007Sci...318.1125W }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |bibcode=2016LPI....47.1869O |title=Radar Sounding by MARSIS over Lucus Planum, Mars |journal=Lunar and Planetary Science Conference |issue=1903 |pages=1869 |last1=Orosei |first1=R. |last2=Cantini |first2=F. |last3=Caprarelli|first3=G. |last4=Carter|first4=L. M. |last5=Papiano |first5=I. |last6=Rossi|first6=A. P.|year=2016 }}</ref>。通过使用火星全球气候模型模拟，以劳拉·克伯(Laura Kerber)为首的一组研究人员发现，梅杜莎槽沟层可能形成于[[阿波里那山|阿波里那山]]、[[阿尔西亚山|阿尔西亚山]]和[[帕弗尼斯山|帕弗尼斯山]]所喷发的火山灰<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/j.icarus.2012.03.016 |title=The dispersal of pyroclasts from ancient explosive volcanoes on Mars: Implications for the friable layered deposits |journal=Icarus |volume=219 |issue=1 |pages=358–381 |year=2012 |last1=Kerber |first1=Laura |last2=Head |first2=James W. |last3=Madeleine |first3=Jean-Baptiste |last4=Forget |first4=François |last5=Wilson |first5=Lionel |bibcode=2012Icar..219..358K }}</ref>。相关的细粒成分提供了进一步证据。该地区几乎没有雷达回波，鉴于这一原因，它也被称为“隐形”区<ref>{{cite book |first=Nadine G. |last=Barlow |title=Mars: an introduction to its interior, surface and atmosphere|url=https://archive.org/details/marsintroduction00barl_258|publisher=[[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]] |location=Cambridge, UK |date=2008 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/marsintroduction00barl_258/page/n84 75]–76|isbn=978-0-521-85226-5}}</ref>。该地层被划分为上、中、下三个子单元区，都属于[[亚马逊纪|亚马逊纪]]，为火星地质史上最年轻的时代<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.3133/i1802B |title=Geologic map of the eastern equatorial region of Mars |first1=Ronald |last1=Greeley |first2=J.E. |last2=Guest |year=1987 }}</ref>。其元素成分的比较表明，梅杜莎槽沟层是火星表面尘埃的主要来源地<ref name=pmid30030425/>。2018年7月，研究人员报告称，事实上，[[火星|火星]]上最大单一尘埃来源地为梅杜莎槽沟层<ref name=pmid30030425/>。

